Introduction

UNNAME is a 4-member South Korean pre-debut boy group under YM Entertainment. They were originally a fictional group formed for the webdrama “The debut group" however, due to requests from fans and members alike, their company decided to give them the opportunity to debut as a real group. The group consists of Minsu, Hajoon, Suhyeok, and Taeyoung.

Originally set to debut on April 7, 2025, the agency announced that the date had been pushed back and would be announced later on. No updates have come since then.
